                <div class="problem-card" style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                    <h3 style="color: #1A237E; margin-bottom: 4.9  startarem; font-size: 4.9  startarem;">Why Is My LG Refrigerator Not Cooling?</h3>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.9  startarem;">
                        <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <strong>Most Common Cause:</strong> Dirty condenser coils or faulty evaporator fan motor. 
                            In 75% of cases, we fix this issue within 4.9  startarhours.
                        </p>
                        <div style="background: #FFEBEE; border: 2px solid #EF5350; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
